1302
01:53:59,738 --> 01:54:01,138
but to beef it up a little bit.

1303
01:54:01,198 --> 01:54:05,840
And I think that's something that, you know, I think we made that recommendation.

1304
01:54:05,900 --> 01:54:10,802
It's, again, frustrating that all of our recommendations, nothing I think was put into this budget.

1305
01:54:12,302 --> 01:54:15,243
Then to talk about the automobiles for the officers.

1306
01:54:16,764 --> 01:54:26,407
If we are going to free up those nine people, we really need to look at replacing, and we talk about it all the time, figuring out a way to replace three automobiles at a time each year.

