We have no leak detection program that the Water and Sewer Commission approved probably about a year, almost a year ago now.

1313
01:54:57,028 --> 01:54:57,928
With regards, I think

1314
01:54:58,328 --> 01:55:04,970
I think others will comment on this, but the $400,000 that the city and the schools use for water, I think that should be in the city budget.

1315
01:55:04,990 --> 01:55:07,431
I think you're just double taxing the rate payer.

1316
01:55:08,791 --> 01:55:15,154
And with regards to just the simple request to get a speed limit monitoring sign, we have one, and ours is broken.

1317
01:55:15,634 --> 01:55:25,877
It's probably the number one complaint I get with regards to speeding, and that removable sign does...

1318
01:55:28,730 --> 01:55:30,931
It's definitely worth it, and we don't have one that's working.

1319
01:55:31,031 --> 01:55:34,872
Ours has been broken for a long time, and we have no end in sight.

1320
01:55:36,893 --> 01:55:43,715
Before I start talking about the schools, I want to fully disclose that I have a written disclosure in the city clerk's office.

1321
01:55:43,775 --> 01:55:47,937
I actually sent an updated one in last night, slipped it under the door.

1322
01:55:49,577 --> 01:55:54,379
My mother works for the school department, and so does my sister, so I want to make that full disclosure.

1323
01:55:57,460 --> 01:56:07,562
I think with regards to the kindergarten aids that was brought up, one great thing that has happened to the schools is the security.

1324
01:56:07,602 --> 01:56:13,983
There's been a huge change in security within the last four months, and I want to thank the school committee and superintendent for handling that.

1325
01:56:14,063 --> 01:56:21,045
Now, every time you go into a school, you have to show your ID, the doors are locked, you have to get buzzed in, show your ID, wear a badge.

1326
01:56:21,225 --> 01:56:23,525
It's definitely much, I feel much safer.

1327
01:56:23,545 --> 01:56:26,846
I do it when I go into my child's school, and I do it when I go into the high school.

1328
01:56:27,533 --> 01:56:28,914
I think that's definitely a positive.

1329
01:56:30,455 --> 01:56:42,105
Paying for the Field of Dreams bond on the city side now, where it's always been on the school side, I didn't understand why that's happening, but that's something that the administration has decided wants to be done.

1330
01:56:43,486 --> 01:56:50,352
Kindergarten aides, very, very happy that there are additional kindergarten aides and that we're putting them in full-time.

