What I think is highly unfair is that there are five classrooms within the city at the three other elementary schools that are not going to have full-time kindergarten aides.

1333
01:57:06,157 --> 01:57:11,240
And I think that's something that should have been looked at in depth.

1334
01:57:11,300 --> 01:57:18,224
And I know at the Brooks School, the teachers did request full-time kindergarten aides, and I believe one or two were not given.

1335
01:57:20,505 --> 01:57:24,167
With regards to school maintenance, I think we got a lengthy, lengthy report.

1336
01:57:25,473 --> 01:57:28,215
on all the school maintenance we need to have done.

1337
01:57:29,696 --> 01:57:36,741
Very detailed report based on each school, Curtis, McGlynn, Medford High, broken down.

1338
01:57:36,881 --> 01:57:40,283
And we're talking millions of dollars in maintenance that these schools need.

1339
01:57:40,684 --> 01:57:48,969
And I don't think that the $400,000 for a high school and all of our other elementary and middle schools is enough.

1340
01:57:49,950 --> 01:57:52,572
I've been getting, even within the last week I've gotten

1341
01:57:53,730 --> 01:58:01,334
I've emailed pictures of just broken lights, broken door.

1342
01:58:01,394 --> 01:58:03,095
I've had it at three different schools.

1343
01:58:03,495 --> 01:58:05,156
You have the people talking now.

1344
01:58:05,356 --> 01:58:11,560
People are definitely contacting the city councilors and the school committee and not afraid to open up about their concerns.

1345
01:58:12,020 --> 01:58:15,122
And I think maintenance is a huge, something we really need to tackle.

1346
01:58:15,962 --> 01:58:20,905
I know the cleaning service that we do hire for Medford High, and I believe the McGlynn

1347
01:58:21,459 --> 01:58:23,360
I was told they don't have enough trash bags.

1348
01:58:23,641 --> 01:58:27,123
We're not giving them enough trash bags because we do provide the trash bags.

1349
01:58:28,384 --> 01:58:37,411
No security after 3.30 on the weekends and expecting parents and coaches to patrol and secure our schools I think is unsafe.

1350
01:58:37,911 --> 01:58:42,595
And I think that's definitely something that we should be adding to the budget.

1351
01:58:43,916 --> 01:58:47,078
Last year I did vote for the budget a number of years in a row.

1352
01:58:47,118 --> 01:58:49,240
And last year I did vote against the budget.

1353
01:58:49,627 --> 01:58:55,691
in its entirety because I believe the schools are too top-heavy, and I know one administrative position has been eliminated this year.

1354
01:58:56,312 --> 01:59:06,598
So that's obviously, I think my concern was valid last year, and I think it probably should be taken more seriously.

1355
01:59:07,339 --> 01:59:19,207
And then we go hire a PR rep for 90,000, nothing against the actual person who took the job, but I think that kindergarten aides are far more important

1356
01:59:19,707 --> 01:59:28,349
