02:00:14,786 --> 02:00:27,057
I was yelled at by the superintendent with regards to, I believe, just not to answer my question, I was yelled at by the superintendent that there was a conflict and I shouldn't even be talking about it.

1365
02:00:27,077 --> 02:00:32,422
