1366
02:00:32,562 --> 02:00:33,122
Inflammatory?

1367
02:00:34,143 --> 02:00:34,624
It's the truth.

1368
02:00:44,935 --> 02:00:48,738
So I question what the right answer is with this vote for the budget.

1369
02:00:48,918 --> 02:00:49,899
I see the positives.

1370
02:00:49,959 --> 02:00:50,760
I see the negatives.

1371
02:00:51,080 --> 02:00:52,581
I think it's very hard.

1372
02:00:52,621 --> 02:00:54,362
I like to hear what my colleagues have to say.

1373
02:00:55,143 --> 02:01:00,887
But I just wanted to voice my concerns and give my rundown.

1374
02:01:01,167 --> 02:01:01,448
Thank you.

