02:01:24,278 --> 02:01:27,340
I reside at 20 Metcalf Street in Medford.

1380
02:01:28,401 --> 02:01:35,227
And I just want to begin by saying that, as you know, in the past, I've attended several budget sessions.

1381
02:01:36,083 --> 02:01:42,408
And what I want to do is try to lend some clarification to the process, if I may.

1382
02:01:42,969 --> 02:01:49,534
I know that the council, the city council itself, does not need my comments on this.

1383
02:01:49,834 --> 02:01:51,375
They are all aware of the process.

1384
02:01:52,636 --> 02:02:01,303
But the taxpaying public out there is a group that I'm really addressing these comments to, so they may understand the process.

1385
02:02:02,304 --> 02:02:03,925
And I want to begin by saying that

1386
02:02:05,444 --> 02:02:16,211
