1394
02:03:03,930 --> 02:03:11,413
That is what the city council has done for the past 28 years and will do again for the 29th year.

1395
02:03:12,733 --> 02:03:25,138
The city council will approve the 2017 budget as submitted by the mayor and the struggling people will be separated from more of their money.

1396
02:03:27,639 --> 02:03:32,721
