1399
02:03:49,837 --> 02:03:50,917
How is that for power?

1400
02:03:53,439 --> 02:04:02,504
So anyway, uh, once submitted by the mayor, the budget can be approved only by you, the city council.

1401
02:04:03,765 --> 02:04:05,506
The council has two other options.

1402
02:04:06,426 --> 02:04:11,989
One, reduce a line item, or two, reject a line item.

1403
02:04:13,230 --> 02:04:20,134
The council cannot reduce or reject a particular amount as specified in the expanded explanation.

1404
02:04:21,154 --> 02:04:31,680
It can reduce or reject a line item amount as the line item was submitted by the mayor and the mayor and line

1405
02:04:32,591 --> 02:04:37,233
pardon me, by the mayor and the mayor submitted each department as a line item.

1406
02:04:38,133 --> 02:04:41,175
So a whole department must be reduced.

1407
02:04:42,816 --> 02:04:44,957
No city council wants to do that.

1408
02:04:46,337 --> 02:04:47,578
Last year's 2016 budget was $155 million.

1409
02:04:47,618 --> 02:04:50,239
This year's 2017 budget is $162 million, an increase of four

