1423
02:06:11,858 --> 02:06:17,900
The cost for each and every public employee on average is $93,000 annually.

1424
02:06:18,020 --> 02:06:19,780
That 4.5% budget increase costs every man

1425
02:06:26,979 --> 02:06:31,981
woman and child in Medford, $125 more annually.

1426
02:06:32,601 --> 02:06:38,203
