1427
02:06:40,604 --> 02:06:50,408
So the people in paying this money are expecting services.

1428
02:06:50,948 --> 02:06:56,010
Now, what are the basic services that the people are paying for that we are not getting?

1429
02:06:57,442 --> 02:07:15,253
sidewalk repairs, pothole repairs, tree trunk removal, pedestrian crosswalks painted, underground pipe repairs, reasonable parking costs, street sweeping.

1430
02:07:17,375 --> 02:07:18,195
This is a great one.

1431
02:07:19,436 --> 02:07:27,181
Public room sanitation, public bathroom, that is, public toilet sanitation, police staffing,

1432
02:07:28,333 --> 02:07:41,856
library renovation, how about stopping, stopping the circumventing of proposition two and a half control of waste fraud and abuse and charter review.

1433
02:07:43,376 --> 02:07:45,117
Now there's a great one charter reviews.

1434
02:07:46,177 --> 02:07:49,797
We saw how that was shot down up on beacon Hill just two weeks ago.

1435
02:07:53,178 --> 02:07:56,819
And there are rumors that the

1436
02:07:57,754 --> 02:08:01,257
Politicians in Medford gave some aid to that result.

1437
02:08:03,558 --> 02:08:25,514
Some of the subjects to be discussed by the people in a charter review are ward representation, term limits, larger city council, voter initiatives, voter recall, school committee chairman, city auditor appointed by the council.

1438
02:08:27,193 --> 02:08:27,913
and many others.

1439
02:08:31,175 --> 02:08:36,358
But our Medford City government does not really want charter review.

1440
02:08:39,499 --> 02:08:46,302
So getting back to the beginning of my talk, how important is democracy?

1441
02:08:47,663 --> 02:08:49,584
Democracy is everything.

