2081
02:58:42,854 --> 02:58:44,255
That's the problem I have.

2082
02:58:44,655 --> 02:58:54,441
Why would you take all the security that you just put on and put them on in the same time and leave the rest of the times open?

2083
02:58:54,881 --> 02:58:57,043
Leave access to the building open.

2084
02:58:57,503 --> 02:59:01,385
I don't buy the fact that we don't have security in our parks.

2085
02:59:01,806 --> 02:59:02,546
I don't buy that.

2086
02:59:02,866 --> 02:59:05,408
We have police on the streets, Mr. Superintendent.

2087
02:59:06,735 --> 02:59:10,999
Our high school, as you know, when's the last time you had a bomb scare at one of our parks?

2088
02:59:11,900 --> 02:59:14,663
But we've had several at Meffitt High School recently.

